cs.AR, cs.PF, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the performance limitations of parallelized sequential computing, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) and performance analysis (cs.PF). It also touches upon the implementation technology (cs.DC) and the computing paradigm (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper mentions the concept of "dark silicon" and how it relates to the "dark performance" in many-processor systems, which could fall under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
